            "descriptionRaw": "Focusing the might of the formless wind around her blade, Jean releases a miniature storm, launching opponents in the direction she aims at, dealing massive <color=#80FFD7FF>Anemo DMG</color>.\n\n<color=#FFD780FF>Hold</color>\nAt the cost of continued stamina consumption, Jean can command the whirlwind to pull surrounding opponents and objects towards her front.\nDirection can be adjusted.\nCharacter is immobile during skill duration.\n\n<i>That which follows Jean, the wholehearted defender, is a guardian wind that can banish danger from her comrades' presence.</i>",
            "name": "Gale Blade"
        },
